  "texts": [
    "Formally, the input consists of two molecular graphs",
    ", where a i: V i → Σ denotes the atom type and b i: E i → {1, 1.5, 2} specifies the bond type (single, aromatic, or double), for i ∈ {1, 2}.",
    "The task is to compute the maximum weight common edge subgraph",
    "Here, Σ is the set of elements, such as Σ = {C, H, N, O, P, S, B, F, Si, Cl, Se, Br, I}.",
    "We reformulate this term and alternatively minimize"
  ]
